  <h4><b>MS IN COUNSELING - Clinic Mental Health Counseling</b></h4>
  <p style="text-align: center"><u>Informed Consent for Video/Audio Recording</u></p>
  <div style="border: black 1px solid">


  As a graduate student, I am required to be under the direct supervision of qualified clinical
    supervisors. My supervisors review all aspects of the services that I am providing to you. You have the
